  "notes": [
    "TMR0 is an 8-bit timer supporting internal FCPU, T0CKI edge, and 32.768KHz external low-speed clock.",
    "10-bit PWM is an independent module; PWM0~PWM3 share a period register; PWM4 has its own.",
    "Comparator supports internal VR and 1.2V BG.",
    "ADC is 12-bit SAR, supports VDD or internal LDO reference."
  ]
